THERMOCOUPLE OPERATION

Ensure you have installed the "Adafruit MAX31855 library" from the Arduino IDE
If not, here are the steps:
  1. Start your Arduino IDE
  2. Click "Tools" -> "Manage Libraries"
  3. Search "Adafruit MAX31855" and install

Make sure your arduino is connected to the computer, Verify the code, and upload.
You are done. Switch over to Python IDE and "csvplotter.py" and "plotter.py"
